thread.title: Yusuf Salih
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Yusuf Salih

author: Yusuf Salih
title: Yusuf Salih
text: I can not fault Store DJ. I called through to the Sydney store, was advised a product specialist from Melbourne would contact me. The advise they provided was spot on, they tracked down the item I needed and supplied it at a competitive price. Fantastic service, would highly recommend.
